item.title: BVMMR Dataset v2
item.description: This dataset includes 4858 fully annotated frontal images of 5991 vehicles from 28 different make and models. Total size 1.38 GB. Note Please cite this paper if you have used the dataset. Download : Part1 Part2 Part3 Part4

item.title: BVMMR Dataset v1
item.description: This dataset includes 676 fully annotated images of 19 different make and models from frontal and rear views of vehicles. There are two views of each image (frontal and rear). Total size 250.6 MB. Note Please cite this paper if you have used the dataset. Download : Dataset MATLAB helper function for reading the annotation files
